additional_house_rules:
AFTER BOOKING: 
After your reservation is accepted, we will email you a welcome letter with all the necessary information about the apartment. Please feel free to ask for any additional information.
CHECK IN – CHECK OUT:
Check in is after 3PM and check out is before 11AM. We can be flexible with check in and check out. For early check in or late check out we will always try to make that possible, but if Apt is booked by other guests it will depend on their schedules. We cannot hold bags in the Apt but can provide 3rd party services.
GENERAL RULES:
We want you to enjoy your stay with us but we ask that all guests be mindful and courteous of others living in the building. As a courtesy, please do not make excessive noise in the hallway when entering or exiting the building. -- Noise to be kept to a minimum between the hours of 9PM and 9AM.
-No smoking anywhere on the property/ building.
-No Candles.
-No pets.
-No loud parties.

$100 dollar fee for lost keys taken from security deposit

If your stay is 10 days or more, we require 1 additional cleaning.
Thank for your understanding!
